data.description: This delightful townhome features new HVAC and a welcoming interior that includes both carpet and tile flooring. The living room is cozy with a fireplace, creating a perfect environment for relaxation. The formal dining area is ideal for enjoying gourmet meals. The kitchen is well-equipped with ample cabinets, SS appliances, glossy counters, and a convenient serving window to the dining area. The main bedroom offers a sitting area and a private bathroom with dual sinks, a soothing tub, and a mirror-door closet. Additionally, the second bedroom provides direct access to the backyard. This outdoor space is serene, featuring a covered patio and a storage room for extra belongings. The community amenities include a pool and spa. This rare two-story townhome is truly a gem. Don't miss it
